  "remarks": "CMRBank is a financial institution active and operational in the illegally annexed territories of Donetsk, Luhansk, Kherson and Zaporizhzhia since October 2022. It is one of the banks in these regions participating in the exchange of hryvnias for roubles for local citizens, as well as for providing preferential loans.",
